<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Sep1940"><font color="red">14 September 1940</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Jacques Mercanton): The German authorities have given me to understand verbally that they would grant my daughter permission to leave the occupied zone &hellip; It remains to be seen also whether the exit permit from the unoccupied zone for which we have applied to the French authorities will be granted us and when </div>
